{"tid":710523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"訓唔著9up","createTime":"2018-06-20T20:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T21:36:58.000Z","uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62241e926fc6290a81c0ab5e4f5f96023204c862","tid":710523,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T20:59:59.000Z","msg":"訓唔著諗起樣野想分享下<br />\n<br />\n岩岩畢業揾左3個月工<br />\n<br />\n有日心血來潮裝香比我老豆求佢保佑我揾到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時好日都唔裝一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住當日interview完 就即時通知我3日後有下輪面試<br />\n<br />\n然後面完第2輪 過一日就比offer 通知我簽約 <br />\n成個過程唔洗一個星期 好順利 感覺個上司又幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我係依次interview之前 好似都衰左10次8次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b166eb450e3454fb35ab0f9ff1bcf07b9dbad6","tid":710523,"uid":56687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:02:48.000Z","msg":"共勉之 巴打"},{"pid":"fe356071b2a58ce170cb5546a7394f83156eb927","tid":710523,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b166eb450e3454fb35ab0f9ff1bcf07b9dbad6","tid":710523,"uid":56687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:02:48.000Z","msg":"共勉之 巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:03:50.000Z","msg":"你唔好咁顛 5點幾都mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee95319f53e9bd2413a76b73647e3d798f22130","tid":710523,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:36:58.000Z","msg":"咁就開始日日裝啦"}]}